<specimenCount box="[354,466,142,166]" pageId="12" pageNumber="169" type="generic" typeStatus="types">two types</specimenCount>
of caudal cilia, of dierent length, both directed backwards. The long cilia in the oral polykinetid develop a velum.
</paragraph>
